*--------------------------------
*   BEEPN.DOC
*---------------------------------------
*   BEEPN = Sound N beeps
*---------------------------------------

    BEEPN is a program for use in batch files
    to cause n beeps to be sounded to signal the user that something
    needs attention.

    syntax :
              BEEPN       ( 1 beep )
              BEEPN n     ( 1 - 9 beeps )

    ( if n is missing, then n defaults to 1 )
    ( if n is < 1 or > 9, then n defaults to 1 )

